You can start offline with static datasets, then later add live APIs.

Hotels & Reviews:

Booking.com / Expedia hotel review datasets (Kaggle). Fields: star rating, user rating, price range, amenities, location.

Attractions/POIs:

TripAdvisor reviews (Kaggle), Open Tourist Attractions datasets, city POI CSVs.

Open Data:

OpenStreetMap (via exports) for coordinates/categories; city open data portals for opening hours.

User Signals (optional): anonymized click/like logs you collect.

ETL Notes:

Normalize cities to ISO codes; geocode missing lat/lng; dedupe by fuzzy name + geo radius.

Compute embeddings once; schedule weekly refresh.

Create derived columns: price_bucket, family_friendly, best_for_rainy_day.
